      "content": "i’ve tried the meds and the therapy stuff but nothing ever works. it feels like my brain is just fundamentally broken. can u explain the actual neuroscience of why some people just can’t recover? like is there a point where the neurochemistry is just too far gone to ever feel anything again?",
